- [Demo Online](#)
- [Github](#)



## Install Plugin
```shell
deepnlpf --install spacy
```


## Install SpaCy Language English
```shell
python -m spacy download en_core_web_sm
```
To install other language models see [here](https://spacy.io/usage).



## Pipeline
<!--DOCUSAURUS_CODE_TABS-->

<!--Json--> 
```json
{
    "lang": "en",
    "tools": [
        {
            "spacy": {
                "pipeline": [
                    "pos",
                    "tag",
                    "shape",
                    "is_alpha",
                    "is_title",
                    "like_num",
                    "label",
                    "noun_chunks"
                ]
            }
        }
    ]
}
```

<!--yaml-->
```yaml
---
lang: en
tools:
- spacy:
    pipeline:
    - pos
    - tag
    - shape
    - is_alpha
    - is_title
    - like_num
    - label
    - noun_chunks
```
